  "texts": [
    "Initially, five existing models are trained and tested: MobileNetV2, Incep-tionV3, AlexNet, VGG16, and ResNet50.",
    "Due to the highest accuracy of InceptionV3, it was selected and further refined to create the AlzheimerNet model using the RMSprop optimizer.",
    "It is implemented using Python, OpenCV, NumPy, and sci-kit learn on a system having AMD Ryzen 7 3800X CPU, and MD Radeon RX580 series GPU achieving an accuracy of 98.68%.",
    "The model achieves significantly higher performance in comparison to the five existing models.",
    "The hybrid model based on PET and fMRI datasets from ADNI to diagnose AD is an option but not used."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}